sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Model
    participant A as Application
    participant T as Tool
    U->>M: question
    M-->>A: AIMessage.tool_calls
    A->>A: allowlist + validate + authorize
    A->>T: execute with timeout
    T-->>A: result or error
    A->>M: ToolMessage(tool_call_id)
    M-->>U: final response
